<div class="container">
    <MudPaper Class="classified-paper">
        <MudGrid Spacing="8" Justify="Justify.Center">
            <MudItem xs="1">
                <MudImage Src="/img/Lot51CoreLibraryLogo.png" Width="64" Height="64" ObjectPosition="ObjectPosition.Center" />
            </MudItem>
            <MudItem xs="11">
                <MudTextM3 Typo="TypoM3.Title">
                    You've heard of an Injector... but... a Prejector?
                </MudTextM3>
                <MudTextM3>
                    We’re working with <MudLink OnClick="Lot51OnClickHandlerAsync">Lot 51</MudLink> to make a version of their <MudLink OnClick="Lot51CoreLibraryOnClickHandlerAsync">Core Library</MudLink> even more powerful by freeing it from the limitations of the game and letting it run right here, inside PlumbBuddy!
                </MudTextM3>
            </MudItem>
        </MudGrid>
    </MudPaper>
    <MudPaper Class="classified-paper">
        <MudGrid Spacing="8" Justify="Justify.Center">
            <MudItem xs="1">
                <MudIcon Icon="@MaterialDesignIcons.Normal.AccountQuestion" Color="Color.Info" Style="padding-left: 4px; padding-top: 6px; width: 64px; height: 64px;" />
            </MudItem>
            <MudItem xs="11">
                <MudTextM3 Typo="TypoM3.Title">
                    But... what does it mean for you as a player?
                </MudTextM3>
                <MudTextM3>
                    It will make your load times faster, make your mods more stable, and give mod creators the ability to bring you even richer experiences in the game than they already can.
                </MudTextM3>
            </MudItem>
        </MudGrid>
    </MudPaper>
    <MudPaper Class="classified-paper">
        <MudGrid Spacing="8" Justify="Justify.Center">
            <MudItem xs="1">
                <MudIcon Icon="@MaterialDesignIcons.Normal.EmoticonExcited" Color="Color.Success" Style="padding-top: 6px; width: 64px; height: 64px;" />
            </MudItem>
            <MudItem xs="11">
                <MudTextM3 Typo="TypoM3.Title">
                    Want to know what you can do while you wait?
                </MudTextM3>
                <MudTextM3>
                    Hyped and want to show your support?
                    Go sub to <MudLink OnClick="Lot51PatreonOnClickHandlerAsync">Lot 51’s Patreon</MudLink>.
                    You can also help by getting the word out about PlumbBuddy for the features you already enjoy.
                    The more Simmers using it, the better the Prejector will be!
                </MudTextM3>
            </MudItem>
        </MudGrid>
    </MudPaper>
